1. Product Vision
What problem does this product solve?
A fun place to practice and study real life cases in a general Vet clinic
Who is it for?
Experienced vets that want to practice or student vets that want to have a more fun approach to study cases.
What makes it different?
It’s a web-based educational platform where veterinary students and practicing veterinarians improve clinical reasoning skills through realistic veterinary cases, in an interactive way. Also a user base to share cases that can be implemented in the game for continuous updated cases. Progress based and leaderboards so they can keep track of their performance.
2. Success Criteria
How will I know the prototype is successful?
•	My girlfriend enjoys using it
•	Users complete cases
•	Users understand learning points

