4. Core User Journey
Step 1: User can log in or creates profile
(Step 1.2): After profile creation and email confirmation, they personalize their profile by choosing avatar (lgbtq gender friendly forms)
Step 2: user gets a prompt in the main page to start first case
Step 2.3: first cas eis always the same case for every user, 
Step 3: User goes into conversation with owner, owner has text bubble to explain the complaints. User can proceed to see the patient information
Step 4: User has to decide which department it should go to/ which examination should be done as first step
Step 5: user then can order diagnostic results and review
Step 6: user has to chose treatment plan based on options given
Step 7: user receives outcome and educational feedback
Step 8: User earns Pawsomemeter points for each case solved

