8. Pawsome-meter System
How are points earned?
Complete case: +3% +1 paw point
Perfect case: increase: +5% + 3 paw points
How are POINTS/PROGRESS FROZEN?
By not playing for a certain amount of time,  like less then 3 times a week. Not playing or many wrong answers just means no progress. 
What happens at 100 points?
When user reaches 100% on the meter they get 1 rank up. It resets the meter and they receive 100 paw points, the currency, and the amount of meters they got filled gives them badges
They can unlock hospital teams, pets and pet clothes.

